---
title: "US50 — Accept / reject service requests"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>RequestsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>AcceptServiceRequest
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: open a pending request
  alt accept
    B->>C: accept(requestId)
    C->>G: update status = accepted
    B-->>A: client notified, work begins
  else reject
    B->>C: reject(requestId)
    C->>G: update status = cancelled
    B-->>A: request closed
  end
